---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Motifs de consultation | Charles-Antoine Menanteau"
  description="Motifs de consultation: anxiete, burn-out, addictions, troubles alimentaires, trauma, deuil et perte de sens."
  currentPath="/motifs"
>
  <section class="page-hero-grid">
    <div class="page-hero-copy">
      <p class="page-eyebrow">Motifs de consultation</p>
      <h1>Des difficultes differentes, une meme attention a ce qui se vit.</h1>
      <span class="heading-rule"></span>
      <p class="page-intro">
        La consultation peut concerner des moments de souffrance psychique, de crise, d'epuisement
        ou de questionnement existentiel. Chaque situation est accueillie dans sa singularite.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="page-hero-visual">
      <div class="page-hero-art page-hero-art-motifs"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dynamic-grid page-section">
    <details class="content-card dynamic-panel">
      <summary class="dynamic-summary">
        <span>
          <span class="dynamic-kicker">Anxiété</span>
          <span class="dynamic-heading">Anxiete et stress</span>
        </span>
        <span class="dynamic-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <p>Crises d'angoisse, tension interieure, sentiment de debordement, inquietude persistante.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="content-card dynamic-panel">
      <summary class="dynamic-summary">
        <span>
          <span class="dynamic-kicker">Épuisement</span>
          <span class="dynamic-heading">Burn-out et depression</span>
        </span>
        <span class="dynamic-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <p>Epuisement psychique, perte d'elan, retrait, difficulte a retrouver des reperes et une energie vitale.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="content-card dynamic-panel">
      <summary class="dynamic-summary">
        <span>
          <span class="dynamic-kicker">Dépendances</span>
          <span class="dynamic-heading">Addictions</span>
        </span>
        <span class="dynamic-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <p>Dependances, repetitions, conduites d'echappement et rapport difficile a la limite ou au manque.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="content-card dynamic-panel">
      <summary class="dynamic-summary">
        <span>
          <span class="dynamic-kicker">Corps</span>
          <span class="dynamic-heading">Troubles alimentaires</span>
        </span>
        <span class="dynamic-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <p>Rapport conflictuel au corps, a l'alimentation, au controle ou a la regulation emotionnelle.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="content-card dynamic-panel">
      <summary class="dynamic-summary">
        <span>
          <span class="dynamic-kicker">Événement</span>
          <span class="dynamic-heading">Trauma</span>
        </span>
        <span class="dynamic-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <p>Evenements difficiles, traces persistantes, etat d'alerte, sidération ou envahissement emotionnel.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="content-card dynamic-panel">
      <summary class="dynamic-summary">
        <span>
          <span class="dynamic-kicker">Sens</span>
          <span class="dynamic-heading">Deuil et perte de sens</span>
        </span>
        <span class="dynamic-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <p>Separations, ruptures, morts, remaniements de vie, crises existentielles et passages interieurs.</p>
    </details>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
